name: NetShop Internet Services
overview:
Since 2004, Netshop-Isp has been a privately owned and operated company specializing in Internet hosting solutions. From shared web hosting and dedicated server hosting to web design and development services, Netshop-Isp has established a solid reputation of offering quality services at affordable pricing.

Today Netshop-Isp is a leading web hosting and web development company in Cyprus and one of the fastest growing providers in Europe. The wide array of web hosting services such as virtual private servers, cloud hosting, dedicated servers and collocation hosting has made us one of the most preferred, reputable and solid providers in Cyprus and abroad.
